highlights.text: Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “צמוד צמוד” is the highest at #2.
“ראיתי עולם” by Omer Adam and ShrekDiMC is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #5.
“נשימה” by Chen Aharoni is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 56 spots at #133.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 325 weeks straight.
